name: Sofia
overview:
Sofia Furniture is an Australian online furniture retailer.

Sofia Furniture was founded with a simple vision: to create beautiful, comfortable and quality furniture at a revolutionary price point.

A collaboration between two brothers and our loyal boxer Sofia; Sofia Furniture was conceived as an alternative to the overpriced and bland sofas available today. By circumventing traditional retail channels and engaging with customers directly through our website, We are able to provide designer furniture up to 70% off traditional retail prices.
